 Then you can import the   CmdBar  Compound Component in your project.     import   { CmdBar }   from   'cmd-bar'    <  CmdBar   :groups="groupedCommands"   />     <  CmdBar.Dialog  >       <  template   #header>         <CmdBar.Input   placeholder  =  "search fo anything />       </template>       <template #content>         <CmdBar.List :config="  listConfig">             <template   #default="{   command   }">               <div   class  =  "leading"  >                 <  img   :src="command.leading"   alt  =  "icon"   />                 {{ command.label }}               </  div  >               <  span   v-if  =  "command.shortcut"   class  =  "actions"  >                 <  kbd   v-for  =  "shortcut of command.shortcut)"   :key="shortcut">                   {{ shortcut }}                 </kbd>               </span>             </template>         </CmdBar.List>       </template>     </CmdBar.Dialog>   </CmdBar>  Setup Nuxt   Add   cmd-bar  dependency to your project:      npm   install   cmd-bar     yarn   add   cmd-bar    pnpm add cmd-bar
